Use case copied from INF-3172:

{quote}After discussing whether or not allowing an empty import of attributes made sense, Jacob described an interesting use case. He said that in some situations, you may just want to import the links. The use case he was referring to was having a project that had a big data store - the ship avails for every ship in the navy. CEC would like to get information about the ship avails, but they only care about the avails for the ships that they deploy to. Pulling all of the avails would clutter up their data with stuff they don't care about.{quote}

